events.name: Future Fridays: You Sure or Not?
events.description:
*Please note the change of location and change in start time*

Over the course of 5 weeks, we have been exploring various  factors that affect our decisionmaking. This week, we will be consolidating our insights, and using those to develop a card game that will test our ability to quickly assess information in every day situations. Are you up for the challenge? 

This game will then travel to HDB locations (as well as anywhere else you like!) -- who will be the most sure of them all?
events.location: Starbucks @ University Town: 8 College Avenue West #B1-01 (Education Resource Centre) Singapore 138608,

events.name: Design a future that you want!
events.description:
Are you someone who just graduated from school? just got your first job? or someone who have been working for years? Ever taught what are the purpose of doing the above? If your answer is to 'EARN INCOME', you are not alone! However, in order for you to be able to enjoy your income, proper money management in crucial. Learn how you can grow your income despite of your busy schedule.
This event will discuss:
- Ways you can multiply your income for your future
- Best instrument to accumulate your savings
- How to protect your income from unforeseen situation
events.location: Parkview Square, 600 North Bridge Road, Singapore 188778
